For git, use link instead of copy; NVM ~ use include since you need to overwrite stuff

Use $HOME instead of ~

Config VIM

Add #!/bin/bash to all files that need it


## Use this
BASEDIR="$(cd "$(dirname "${BASH_SOURCE[0]}")" && pwd)"

# vim
ln -s ${BASEDIR}/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ${BASEDIR}/vim/ ~/.vim

# zsh
ln -s ${BASEDIR}/zshrc ~/.zshrc

# git
ln -s ${BASEDIR}/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
